name: SCIPUrinaryDiversionProcedures
title: SCIP urinary diversion procedures
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains  urinary diversion procedures.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have had a urinary diversion procedure.  Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Procedure category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include ICD 10 PCS codes that identify procedures to divert the flow of urine, including conduit and reservoir construction procedures.),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude codes that do not meet the inclusion criteria.)
